Package actions

Various wrappers and their annotation definitions for handling requests from different sources.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    APICallAction
    Default wrapper for requests done by the portal
    MobileCallAction
    request wrapper for requests from external services
    VisualizationCallAction
    Default wrapper for requests done by plugins
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    APICall
    Annotation for the default request wrapper
    MobileCall
    Annotation for use of the request wrapper for calls from external services
    VisualizationCall
    Annotation for using the wrapper for plugin calls
